Package com.tangosol.util

Class SafeSortedMap

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractMap
java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentSkipListMap
com.tangosol.util.SafeSortedMap
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, ConcurrentMap, ConcurrentNavigableMap, Map, NavigableMap, SequencedMap, SortedMap
@Deprecated public class SafeSortedMap extends ConcurrentSkipListMap
Deprecated.
use NullableConcurrentMap instead.
Implementation of a SortedMap extending ConcurrentSkipListMap to support null keys and null values. Note that unlike its super class, this class is not serializable.
Since:
23.03
Author:
mg
